，或者就直接私聊那个小朋友家长了，我让宝宝自己去问就是让他们小孩子的事情自己解决，找不到是可以算了，但是自己要学会先去尝试一下怎么寻找。第三、宝宝不敢去问，不会用办法去找，我不鼓励他教导他迈出这一步，还要让他楞楞的放弃，遗忘吗？ 然后媳妇就觉得我小气，计较，会把娃娃也教成这样，我就说直来直去，简简单单一个事怎么有那么复杂？又不是工作群，同学群，我还得考虑那么多？现在人都很直爽了吧。 然后，我们吵翻了。 我就想问问大家，这个事情你们怎么看？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-3f453fc2fa969800a5fbd354135cad95_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/484999894"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I2J2h6/PZ3MtrEAMaCDcwMDU5NjQyIKL81YkGMAI4J0Aecgk0ODQ5OTk4OTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1631160523.5091662", "card_id": "Q_413851618", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 250}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2021 年有哪些高性价比的手机值得推荐？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "快来看看 2021 年有哪些手机值得购买！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-9496a4d9a306e56f584fad14f6c8b65e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/413851618"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2J2h6/PZ3MtrEAMaCDU0MjQ0NTczILSk0PkFMAQ45wZAH3IJNDEzODUxNjE4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1631160523.5095696", "card_id": "Q_484187589", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "罗云熙的古装扮相如何？为什么会受到许多人的喜欢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-dbd418d65169182b18451f4fcd3df769_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/484187589"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I2J2h6/PZ3MtrEAMaCDY5ODc5MTMzIK6TwYkGMAU4MUAgcgk0ODQxODc1ODl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1631160523.509914", "card_id": "Q