制造魔法伤害。薇古丝可以再次施放本技能，命令「暗影」把她拉到被标记的目标处，制造额外魔法伤害。 若被标记的目标在受到「愁煞」伤害不久后阵亡，则薇古丝能在几秒内再次施放「愁煞」。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9e42c01df326b1db4aef093275e92b5e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/484449552"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2J2h6/PZ3MtrEAMaCDY5OTM3NTU1IM36xokGMAc4pAFAJnIJNDg0NDQ5NTUyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1631160523.514089", "card_id": "Q_484812992", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 49}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "不想被钟离养成废物，各位能教我怎么玩游戏《原神》吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "55 级玩家想改过自新"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c2a6dc2e91873384dc7828bad862ca6c_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/484812992"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI2J2h6/PZ3MtrEAMaCDcwMDE4MjMzIK650IkGMAE4MkAncgk0ODQ4MTI5OTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1631160523.5146685", "card_id": "Q_19852536", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 233}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "考托福、雅思、 GRE 对不出国的人有什么意义？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-86a299fd80818591f5363b6ea8071697_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/19852536"}}, "attached_info": "CjwI2J2h6/PZ3MtrEAMaBjEyMDkwNyDs1M/zBDAUOKlRQChyCDE5ODUyNTM2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1631160523.515172", "card_id": "Q_484981791", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 104}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待徐雷升任京东总裁，刘强东将把更多时间投入乡村振兴